<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-15"><a href="Hinduism#Beliefs"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Beliefs</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-16"><a href="Hinduism#Purusharthas_(objectives_of_human_life)"><span class="tocnumber">4.1</span> <span class="toctext">Purusharthas (objectives of human life)</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-3 tocsection-17"><a href="Hinduism#Dharma_(righteousness,_ethics)"><span class="tocnumber">4.1.1</span> <span class="toctext">Dharma (righteousness, ethics)</span></a></li>
