<p>Demographically, Hinduism is the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Major_religious_groups" title="Major religious groups">world's third largest religion</a>, after <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christianity" title="Christianity">Christianity</a> and <a href="Islam" title="Islam">Islam</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-709" class="reference"><a href="Hinduism#cite_note-709">&#91;web 38&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-710" class="reference"><a href="Hinduism#cite_note-710">&#91;618&#93;</a></sup>
</p>
