</li>
<li id="cite_note-160"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Hinduism#cite_ref-160">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Sweetman cites Dirks (2001), <i>Castes of Mind: Colonialism and the Making of Modern India</i>, Princeton University Press, p. xxvii</span>
