<li id="cite_note-289"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Hinduism#cite_ref-289">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Rigveda is not only the oldest among the vedas, but is one of the earliest <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indo-European_languages" title="Indo-European languages">Indo-European</a> texts.</span>
