<li id="cite_note-Entwistle1987-642"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Hinduism#cite_ref-Entwistle1987_642-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFEntwistle1987" class="citation book">Entwistle, A. W. (1 January 1987). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=2YoRAQAAIAAJ"><i>Braj: Centre of Krishna pilgrimage</i></a>. E. Forsten. pp.&#160;125, 319–320.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Braj%3A+Centre+of+Krishna+pilgrimage&amp;rft.pages=125%2C+319-320&amp;rft.pub=E.+Forsten&amp;rft.date=1987-01-01&amp;rft.aulast=Entwistle&amp;rft.aufirst=A.+W.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D2YoRAQAAIAAJ&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHinduism" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-643"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Hinduism#cite_ref-643">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFDunlopSykesJackson2001" class="citation web">Dunlop, Fiona; Sykes, Carol; Jackson, Felicity (2001). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=AnLWgVtbJpoC">"Fodor's Exploring India"</a>. Fodor's Travel Publications. p.&#160;135. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-679-00707-4" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-679-00707-4"><bdi>978-0-679-00707-4</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Fodor%27s+Exploring+India&amp;rft.pages=135&amp;rft.pub=Fodor%27s+Travel+Publications&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-679-00707-4&amp;rft.aulast=Dunlop&amp;rft.aufirst=Fiona&amp;rft.au=Sykes%2C+Carol&amp;rft.au=Jackson%2C+Felicity&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DAnLWgVtbJpoC&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHinduism" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
